FT  22 JAN 94 / Markets: FT Quarterly Review - At a glance
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
To most people, the benefits of investing offshore are far from clear. But
Kenneth Clarke's Budget did make one tax change that could give offshore
funds an advantage. The winter issue of the FT Quarterly Review of Personal
Finance, to be published with next Friday's paper and repeated with
Saturday's, considers the pros and cons of five types of offshore
investment. The survey section of the review focuses on domestic finance
matters, including school fees, the cost of going to university and paying
for a wedding.
