Turnover of John D Wood, the estate agent, expanded 36 per cent from Pounds
2.37m to Pounds 3.22m and resulted in a return to profits with Pounds
369,000 at the pre-tax level for the six months to October 31, compared with
losses last time of Pounds 77,000.
