interim of 0.75p.
All eight of the group's London sales offices performed well, 'the market
having improved at all levels with the number of of sales increasing by over
50 per cent', directors pointed out.
They added that since the end of October the recovery in volumes and house
prices had been sustained 'and we expect this trend to continue'.
