FT  21 JAN 94 / UK Company News: Hill &amp; Smith shows sharp recovery to Pounds
4m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Hill &amp; Smith, the West Midlands-based steel stockholding, forging and
fabricated products company, reversed its downward spiral with pre-tax
profits sharply increased over the 12 months to September 30.
On turnover marginally ahead to Pounds 67m, profits improved from Pounds
