yesterday that all group business were profitable during the year, except
the forging side and that was expected to return to the black in the next
few months.
Earnings jumped to 9.91p (1.95p) and a final dividend of 4.1p lifts the
total 10 per cent to 6.2p. The group also proposed its usual scrip issue,
this time on a 1-for-10 basis.
